name: AQUARIUM BATTLE - FISH & FEED
description:
There is no horn in in life circles! Explore the depth, discover what the ocean is hiding. There are plenty of wonderful creatures living in the depths. There are also friendly beings and dangerous ones among them. Defend yourself from the predators and collect the treasures to get to the next level. Watch the signs that help you find the crates!



Features:

* varied, multifaceted wildlife
* ferocious beast enemies
* low poly style
* underwater battles
